UK family holidays: summer survival guide Here is our survival guide to the most-family friendly hotels as well the best of what's on in Britain this July and August. Image 1 of 3	A happy crowd at Camp Bestival Image 1 of 3	The Imperial War Museum, London, where the excellent exhibition Once Upon A Wartime is now being held Photo: Alamy	Image 1 of 3	Calcot Manor in Gloucestershire, a very civilised Cotswolds hotel <
